# eKartoteka Sensor 

This sensor is gathering gas usage data for eKartoteka clients regarding utility bills and rental invoices.

It uses API from https://www.e-kartoteka.pl/#/login

The idea of sensor came from great work in https://github.com/pawelhulek/pgnig-sensor/

## Manual Configuration
Sample configuration

```yaml
sensor:
  - platform: ekartoteka_sensor
    username: YOUR USERNAME
    password: YOUR PASSWORD
```
It is recommended to confiure the sensor through the UI.

## Through the interface
1) Navigate to Settings > Devices & Services and then click Add Integration
2) Search for eKartoteka
3) Enter your credentials (e-mail and password)

## Technical Details

The sensor uses API from https://www.e-kartoteka.pl/#/login.

The data is refreshed every 24 hours or on the sensor startup.
The sensors are not updated if the data hasn't changed.

